    "Id": "chassisdef_magpie_MGP-96",
    "Name": "Magpie",
    "Details": "The MGP-96 replaces the stolen technology of the original with legitimate production components, trading the Partial Wing for a more conventional jump package. A Void Signature System powered by an Angel ECM Suite provides substantially stronger stealth capability than the original Guardian setup. Three ER Medium Lasers and two ER Small Lasers give it more direct firepower than the MGP-86, making it a more capable combatant despite losing some jump distance.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stubble Wings</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
